==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Crystallize
<hw>Crys"tal*lize</hw> <pr>(kr⟦icr⟧s"t⟦ait⟧l*l⟦imac⟧z)</pr>, <pos>v.
t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p. p.</pos> <conjf>Crystallized</conjf>
<pr>(-l⟦imac⟧zd)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb. n.</pos>
<conjf>Crystallizing</conjf>.]</vmorph> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>cristalliser</ets>. See <er>Crystal</er>.]</ety> <def>To cause to
form crystals, or to assume the crystalline form.</def>⟦br⟧
